AccountId.description: Unique identifier for the account where the ad group belongs.

CampaignId.description: Unique identifier for the campaign where the ad group belongs.

AdGroupId.description: Unique identifier for the ad group.

TimePeriod.description: Date and time when the data was recorded.

AdDistribution.description: The types of distribution networks where the ad was shown.

DeviceType.description: Type of device where the ad was shown.

Network.description: Type of advertising network where the ad was shown.

DeliveredMatchType.description: Type of match bid used for the keyword delivered with the ad.

DeviceOS.description: Operating system of the device where the ad was shown.

TopVsOther.description: Performance comparison of top ad placements versus other placements.

BidMatchType.description: Type of match bid used for the keyword triggering the ad.

Language.description: Language settings targeting for the ad.

AccountName.description: Name of the account where the ad group belongs.

CampaignName.description: Name of the campaign where the ad group belongs.

Impressions.description: Number of times the ad was shown.

Clicks.description: Number of clicks on the ad.

CostPerConversion.description: Average cost per conversion for specific actions.

ExpectedCtr.description: Expected click-through rate for the ad.

AdRelevance.description: Quality score reflecting how relevant the ad is to the audience.

LandingPageExperience.description: Quality score for the landing page experience.

PhoneImpressions.description: Number of times the phone number was shown in the ad.

PhoneCalls.description: Number of phone calls driven by the ad.

Assists.description: Number of assist impressions for the ad.

CostPerAssist.description: Average cost per assist for the ad.

CustomParameters.description: Custom parameters associated with the ad.

FinalUrlSuffix.description: Suffix added to the final URL for tracking purposes.

ViewThroughConversions.description: Number of view-through conversions attributed to the ad.

AllReturnOnAdSpend.description: Return on investment for all actions taken as a result of the ad.

AllConversions.description: Total number of all conversions from the ad.

AllConversionRate.description: Overall conversion rate for all actions taken as a result of the ad.

AllRevenue.description: Total revenue generated from all conversions.

AllRevenuePerConversion.description: Average revenue generated per all conversion.

AverageCpc.description: Average cost per click for the ad.

AveragePosition.description: The average position of the ad when shown.

Conversions.description: Total number of conversions for specific actions from the ad.

ConversionRate.description: Conversion rate for specific actions taken as a result of the ad.

ConversionsQualified.description: Number of qualified conversions from the ad.

Revenue.description: Total revenue generated from specific actions as a result of the ad.

RevenuePerConversion.description: Average revenue per conversion for specific actions.
